Create Near
SyncState *

####################
# Gmail: martinuzak136@gmail.com
####################

IMAPAccount gmail
Host imap.gmail.com
User martinuzak136@gmail.com
PassCmd "pass show gmail-mbsync"
SSLType IMAPS
AuthMechs LOGIN

IMAPStore gmail-remote
Account gmail

MaildirStore gmail-local
Path ~/Mail/martinuzak136@gmail.com/
Inbox ~/Mail/martinuzak136@gmail.com/Inbox
Subfolders Verbatim

Channel gmail
Far :gmail-remote:
Near :gmail-local:
Patterns INBOX "[Gmail]/Sent Mail" "[Gmail]/Drafts"
Sync Full
Expunge Both


